@node "inst" "Getting this sod to work..."
(1) Copy all files to where they should be.

(2) Check for rexxtricks.library and rexxsupport.library

(3) Tooltypes:

    ANONY_COL= Anonymous name colour
    NORML_COL= Username colour
    ANONY_CFG= 'yes' to enable the anonymous function
    CURSO_OFF= 'yes' to blank cursor from screen
    LINES_CFG= How many wall lines. Be realistic:)
    EDITL_LVL= Level needed for built-in editor

(4)  The current setup is for 15 lines on the wall. If you change
this then it  will  adjust  itself,  adding  or  removing  lines,
which might take a while. After that, it's speed city. Possibly.

(5) Add 'doors:mowall/wall.logo' for top logo if desired.

(6)  Go  through  the  rexx  script itself, adjusting things that
should have been tooltypes also, but I'm fucked man, fucked.

(7) Anonymous entries are saved to 'wall.stat'.
@endnode
